QueryText: how to control field rats ?
KCCAns: Commonly 2% bait is used to kill rats. 2 per cent bait is prepared by mixing 2gm zinc phosphide with 98g of bait. Either cooked rice, or Wheat flour or Grain flour is used for preparing baits and along with this edible oil (mustard oil) is added in small quantities as attractant. Pre baiting with only baiting material is quite essential for attracting the rats to eat.  Rats have to be fed for a period of 5-7 days before they start dying
